"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brazilian chiptune soundtrack</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced matches with easy rematch</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accessibility features: adjustable colors, sound, and screen reader support (NVDA required)</p></li></ul>",
